trans-unit.source: Stores sink provider data for sink providers.

The sink provider data is a tree structure of configuration information stored in the [\<provider> Element (Template)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/d3e67e16-8ca3-4b7f-b7a4-37e3e1a66364) configuration nodes.
trans-unit.target: Sink Providerdata är en trädstruktur Konfigurationsinformationen lagras i den [ \<provider > Element (mall)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/d3e67e16-8ca3-4b7f-b7a4-37e3e1a66364) configuration noder.

trans-unit.source: All sink providers must have a constructor that accepts a <xref:System.Collections.IDictionary> of properties and a <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> of these structures if they want to be used from a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Alla Mottagarproviders måste ha en konstruktor som accepterar en <xref:System.Collections.IDictionary>Egenskaper och en <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>av dessa strukturer om de vill användas från en konfigurationsfil.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection> </xref:System.Collections.IDictionary>
